OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan risked life to save    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgirl from oncoming train   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man risked his life to save a teenage
OL,6, girl who had jumped on to train tracks.
OL,8,FKyle Dovey, a social worker from Old   
OL,9,FColwyn, Conwy county, has been         
OL,10,Frecognised after he pulled the girl to 
OL,11,Fsafety at Colwyn Bay station seconds   
OL,12,Fbefore an oncoming train passed.       
OL,14,FThe girl was badly injured after the   
OL,15,Ftrain hit her while Mr Dovey was trying
OL,16,Fto save her, but she survived.         
OL,18,FMr Dovey is now set to receive the     
OL,19,Frarely awarded Royal Humane Society    
OL,20,FSilver Medal for his bravery.          
